{"tid":935981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Rubio] 美參議員擬提交法案　禁中國電訊商在美國做生意","createTime":"2018-12-10T12:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T06:44:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5ab761426484455488343b7733befbf71c3f11","tid":935981,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:10:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美參議員擬提交法案　禁中國電訊商在美國做生意</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/269247/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%95%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F269247%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F&d=wmRl8O2Sve2obXbrhbLjEP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a397fb6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/269247/%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%93%AC%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E7%A6%81%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%95%86%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%81%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F</a><br />\n<br />\n魯比奧周日（9日）接受哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）電視節目《面向全國》（Face The Nation）採訪時表示，華為和中興通訊（ZTE）等中國公司對美國國家利益和安全構成威脅，自己百分百會向國會提交法案，禁止中國電訊公司在美國做生意。<br />\n<br />\n他表示：「我們必須明白中國企業不像美國企業。我們甚至無法要求蘋果公司在恐怖襲擊案調查中，幫助我們破解iPhone。但在中國，沒有一家公司不需要按照政府要求做事。當中國政府要求一間電訊公司交出在他國營運時所收集到的數據時，這些公司會照做。無法院命令，這些企業卻會從命，我們需要明白這一點。」"},{"pid":"f86c1283e506467651c03214e4c23eb93f4309b4","tid":935981,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa17b4ae7792542200cb109906bb9f173165103e","tid":935981,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c24764b25b6f02e3bc8f09c46bf010f0b8b169b","tid":935981,"uid":58670,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"Rubio 2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056da0befb6a71d486a1d1e531799b9338e8e257","tid":935981,"uid":37586,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"90日停貿易戰,但係每日有其他政策打擊支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那跟唔切呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b08c626c8f9601cf8e09a497b4eadbfff87fef8","tid":935981,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c24764b25b6f02e3bc8f09c46bf010f0b8b169b","tid":935981,"uid":58670,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"Rubio 2020 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T12:14:49.000Z","msg":"2020年美國總統選舉 Marco Rubio支持區（一）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/672285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/672285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse